title: Beautiful Townhome with Garage, 8 Acre Park, Granite, Garden Tubs
posting_body: Beautiful Gated community with an 2 acre park and dog park.
Interiors include hardwood and Italian tile flooring, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, track lighting, stone fireplaces, crown molding, oval spa tubs, and full-size W/D connections.
Amenities include a 2-story clubhouse, pool table, pool and spa, fitness center, business center, enclosed yards, onsite dog park, and 8 acres of parkland.
Next door, access even more amenities, such as indoor basketball and racquetball, lighted tennis, putting green, sand/water volleyball, game room, and playground.
Covered & direct-access garage parking is available.
